UniTrans Notice
===============

This repository contains the official implementation of UniTrans.

Original UniTrans Contributions
-------------------------------

The core UniTrans components, including the modality-intrinsic representation
pretraining pipeline, mapping-conditioned translator expert learning, and
related UniTrans model code, were developed by the UniTrans authors.

